    "data": [
        {
            "title": "預算案2025｜公民科本年度預算達1.16億元  較上年度增加3000萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"公民科今年預算達1.16億元 較去年增加3000萬\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0f056458e7ddd19fa7a34a91e322ff24/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040316041856393.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">公民科今年預算達1.16億元 較去年增加3000萬</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>本港學生到內地交流的計劃越來越多。教育局表示，2024/25學年共有81000名學生參與內地交流計劃，政府開支高達1億1490萬元；公民與社會發展科課程的內地考察方面，2024/25年度考察費用達8620萬元，而2025/26學年預算開支達1.16億元，即增加近3000萬元。\n\n</p><h2>內地交流計劃開支預算1.13億元</h2>\n<p>教育局表示，學生內地交流及考察是國民教育的重要一環，有助學生從多角度親身體會國家不同方面的發展，鞏固和深化課堂學習，以加深他們對國家的認識，提升國民身份認同。在2025/26學年，學生內地交流計劃和公民科內地考察的預算開支分別為1.13億元及1.16億元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175110/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現時有不同的學生內地交流計劃。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/797d8808858e624e4132fb63b111ce62/2025-04/2_7_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現時有不同的學生內地交流計劃。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>學生內地交流計劃  每年約提供10萬個名額</h2>\n<p>教育局指學生內地交流計劃，每年約提供10萬個名額。有關交流計劃在2022/23年度，參加的學生僅600人，而隨著香港與內地恢復全面通關，教育局於2023/24學年重啟學生內地交流計劃，教育局稱學校反應積極，參與人數達68200人，2024/25則再進一步上升至81000人，開支亦由2022/23年度的210萬上升至1億1490萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>公民科方面，2024/25年度約有50400名高中學生，考察費用達8620萬元，較2023/24年49900名學生、7080萬元，支出增加約1540萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2061920/即時-港聞-預算案2025-公民科本年度預算達1-16億元-較上年度增加3000萬",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 16:11:21",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "海關紅磡搗破酒店房間毒品倉 檢$2900萬可卡因拘無業男",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"海關高級調查主任陳杰論展示檢獲的毒品證物。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/abdf7cf5551c258b2faf5fb80cc9f0f3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040316012226834.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">海關高級調查主任陳杰論展示檢獲的毒品證物。蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港海關昨日（2日）在紅磡採取反毒品行動，其間在一間酒店內截查一名可疑男子，並在該名男子手持的膠袋中，檢獲約2公斤可卡因，於是將他拘捕。其後海關人員押解該名男子到酒店房間搜查，再檢獲約32公斤可卡因。案中海關共檢獲34公斤可卡因，總市值約2,900萬元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175122/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉案證物。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/213046f0f78b537dd51dbfe5df180f21/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_02_-_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案證物。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175123/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ecd8abaa999b461e0f4b5c16800b7df/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_03_-_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175124/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/867387a7545e450279c2a47e8289fd14/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_04_-_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175125/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關檢獲的可卡因。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ab470acae258be853b8d1119c62001e1/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關檢獲的可卡因。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175126/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8193a2b959f9293a71535239d34a78e7/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175127/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e2671413890cd3fab55c3af5332ba361/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>被捕的23歲本地男子，報稱無業。海關指出，涉案販毒集團利用相對有規模和較高級的酒店，作為流動毒品儲存倉。這些酒店往往保安嚴密，販毒集團藉酒店的旅客人流企圖掩人耳目，逃避執法人員追查。\n\n</p>\n<p>今次是海關近2星期以來，所破獲的第三宗重大危險藥物案件，三宗案件涉及的毒品總市值約6,900萬元，共拘捕4名人士。海關稱，相信是次行動已搗破區內一個毒品儲存倉庫，案件仍在調查中。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175128/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉案可卡因總值約2,900萬元。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/efc364a1f8637a10838625fb9280c36f/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案可卡因總值約2,900萬元。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175129/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2b89cef336a4c76466bfbd67b6f89fb8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175130/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d08a336f300fcca018b6c300e0086c4b/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_151329793_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175145/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關毒品調查科毒品調查第一組高級調查主任陳杰論。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb1c57cb821f412179456c33d62c45a8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_150927452_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關毒品調查科毒品調查第一組高級調查主任陳杰論。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175147/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ab1e59b1b6a40b1b31982e705d5c5f21/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_150927452_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175148/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/de4bb7e26821e14beda76aa148661d9d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250403_150927452_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
